                maximum measurement range of the laser radar.
              </xs:documentation>
            </xs:annotation>
          </xs:element>
          <xs:element name="MinMeasurementRange"
                      type="LinearValueType"
                      minOccurs="0">
            <xs:annotation>
              <xs:documentation>
                The optional MinMeasurementRange element is the
                minimum measurement range of the laser radar.
              </xs:documentation>
            </xs:annotation>
          </xs:element>
          <xs:element name="ScanningSpeed"
                      type="UserDefinedUnitValueType"
                      minOccurs="0">
            <xs:annotation>
              <xs:documentation>
                The optional ScanningSpeed element is the scanning
                speed of the laser radar.
              </xs:documentation>
            </xs:annotation>
          </xs:element>
          <xs:element name="DistanceAccuracy"
                      type="LinearErrorType"
                      minOccurs="0">
            <xs:annotation>
              <xs:documentation>
                The optional DistanceAccuracy element is the accuracy
                in linear measurements with the laser radar.
              </xs:documentation>
            </xs:annotation>
          </xs:element>
          <xs:element name="AzimuthAngularAccuracy"
                      type="AngularErrorType"
                      minOccurs="0">
            <xs:annotation>
              <xs:documentation>
                The optional AzimuthAngularAccuracy element is the azimuth
                angle accuracy when the laser radar head is rotating. With
                increasing the distance, azimuth angular error increases.
              </xs:documentation>
            </xs:annotation>
          </xs:element>
          <xs:element name="ElevationAngularAccuracy"
                      type="AngularErrorType"
                      minOccurs="0">
            <xs:annotation>
              <xs:documentation>
